mergiraf
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
License:    GNU General Public License v3.0 (GPL-3.0)
Source:     https://codeberg.org/mergiraf/mergiraf

mergiraf is fetched as a prebuilt, unmodified binary at Docker image build
time (see api/Dockerfile) and invoked exclusively as a separate subprocess
by gfix's own `gitfix_conflict_resolve {kind: mergiraf}` tool call. It is
never linked against, vendored, or modified as part of gfix-cloud's own
source code. See docs/adr/0004-mergiraf-subprocess-boundary.md for the
license-boundary rationale.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
gfix
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Source:     https://github.com/ameyypawar/gfix (releases)

The `gfix` binary is fetched from GitHub Releases at Docker image build
time and invoked as a subprocess (`gfix mcp`) via the Model Context
Protocol. gfix is a separate project from gfix-cloud.
